{"tid":1112650,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)達文西密碼1-3","createTime":"2019-04-17T13:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T20:22:14.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6166a7b480b1a6921ce8a89d78bf7215d20afa9","tid":1112650,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=c54e3df5\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=5371706c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=3e4a6bf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9b/The_da_vinci_code.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9b%2FThe_da_vinci_code.jpg&h=16ef5619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.電影由羅浮宮館長雅克&middot;索尼埃（Jacques Sauniere）在館內被一名身穿修道服的持槍男子賽拉斯（Silas）追殺展開，塞拉斯逼問索尼埃拱心石（Priory's clef de voute，或Keystone）的下落，索尼埃與其他三位「守護者」一樣在臨死前撒了同樣的謊，說拱心石在巴黎聖蘇比教堂（Church of Saint-Sulpice）里的羅斯經線（Rose Line）下，塞拉斯信以為真，開槍射中索尼埃的腹部之後離開。與此同時，美國宗教符號學教授羅伯特&middot;蘭登（Robert Langdon，湯姆&middot;漢克斯飾）作為客座講師正在巴黎進行一場關於符號學和女性崇拜（sacred feminine）的演講。法國警方找到了他並將其帶到羅浮宮的案發現場<br />\n<br />\n2.在神父西爾瓦諾&middot;班提佛立歐和科學家維多利亞&middot;威特拉的注視下，歐洲核子研究組織（CERN）啟動大型強子對撞機，並捕捉到三小瓶反物質。過了不久，有人殺死西爾瓦諾，挖去了他的眼球，並用此眼球開啟了放置反物質的密室，進而取走其中一小瓶反物質，而西爾瓦諾的胸膛還被烙上一個神祕的印記<br />\n<br />\n3.哈佛大學教授勞勃&middot;蘭登（湯姆&middot;漢克斯 飾）在義大利佛羅倫斯一家醫院中醒來，他失去了過去幾天前的記憶，還被地球烤焦的鏡像困擾。席耶娜&middot;布魯克醫生（費莉絲蒂&middot;瓊斯 飾）告訴他，一枚子彈穿過他的大腦，造成失憶。隨後，刺客瓦任莎（安娜&middot;烏拉魯）偽裝成警察欲刺殺蘭登，她在通往蘭登病房的過道殺了一位醫生。慌亂中，席耶娜帶著蘭登逃進她的寓所<br />\n<br />\n9 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=209f70f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=96a60a44\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73e2d714553f520aeb9906c3615c144b35c7d51","tid":1112650,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3850fcfb4a021b81dadee749f30b5719360733a4","tid":1112650,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"